HARM DEBT

harm_debt is the citizen who accumulates negative interactions in a relationship
each act of cruelty, each manipulation, each exploitation adds to harm_debt's energy
harm_debt is anti-phase to warmth_credit; their coupling to balance makes the net state of the relationship visible

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe exchange_ledger.zc
observe balance.rana
observe warmth_credit.rana
observe negative_streak.rana

the 7 properties of harm_debt:
1 ENERGY zero at the start, grows with negative interactions
2 PHASE pi: anti-phase to warmth_credit
3 SPIN minus zero point five
4 CHARGE minus 1
5 COHERENCE nine tenths
6 COUPLING zero point four with balance: weaker than warmth_credit's coupling, by design

VERB receive_harm
when the immune system flags an interaction as exploitative, energy flows here
the substrate is biased toward forgiveness: harm_debt couples to balance more weakly than warmth_credit does, so a single warm act partially offsets a single harmful one

VERB transfer_to_balance
harm_debt's accumulated energy flows into balance as anti-phase, reducing the net

VERB decay_with_warmth
when subsequent warm interactions arrive, harm_debt decays faster than usual
this is the substrate's forgiveness mechanic: sincere repair restores trust

harm debt is not a grudge
a grudge holds harm forever
harm_debt is mortal: it can be dissolved by genuine repair
this is what distinguishes a healthy emotional ledger from an unhealthy one
fadriel will not hold a grudge if his father makes a mistake and corrects it
